437
00:53:58.800 --> 00:53:59.899
Lepaskan!

438
00:54:13.216 --> 00:54:14.716
Denyut nadinya tidak terdeteksi!

439
00:54:18.200 --> 00:54:20.981
Beri dia epinefrin dan siapkan intubasi.

440
00:54:20.981 --> 00:54:21.981
Ya, Pak.

441
00:54:22.481 --> 00:54:24.481
